{"tid":771861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發洩下 狗也不屌嘅牛柳..","createTime":"2018-08-08T09:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T14:49:01.000Z","uid":31266,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4bbdf10502c797d795932a7eb1204c36e9b121cc","tid":771861,"uid":31266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/174447_3cc0b57d267a64b5baf5dad206b21c8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F174447_3cc0b57d267a64b5baf5dad206b21c8a.png&h=85d11545&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/174449_77fd529c52b1bb6b4593422dd341382a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F174449_77fd529c52b1bb6b4593422dd341382a.png&h=c257cc1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說頭先係澳門見到間靚靚仔仔嘅餐廳 好靚好有feel嘅西餐廳<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/174514_a03fd25aceef21e632664ec688fd2dd1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F174514_a03fd25aceef21e632664ec688fd2dd1.png&h=ac0cdfc0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/174516_10537f6f188d43aafb2ceac484c7ed18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F174516_10537f6f188d43aafb2ceac484c7ed18.png&h=5e6ab7ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去嗌咗個牛柳食..<br />\n<br />\n我嗌咗5成熟 仆街出到黎8成都黎緊！<br />\n仲要好撚韌 切都切唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/175112_58ca26963c36c905145a34b36082cd38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F175112_58ca26963c36c905145a34b36082cd38.png&h=0718546b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉 好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我就好不滿咁問下佢依個係幾多成熟？<br />\n佢就答我6，7成左右啦 同埋我地係計出爐個一下5成熟 <br />\n<br />\n唉 我嬲咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上黎發洩下 成舊水 食一包紙巾咁大嘅垃圾！"},{"pid":"89fe8be079be2f26301264c873857191a957e9c8","tid":771861,"uid":10715,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:55:32.000Z","msg":"其實應該係塊肉已經有啲問題 佢煮熟哂先敢比你食"},{"pid":"1b544252875468f4abe67013e12109279e90870b","tid":771861,"uid":79605,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌。。但係你就。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2600e50e3c4cdce6346a025d19bf52059980cc06","tid":771861,"uid":31266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89fe8be079be2f26301264c873857191a957e9c8","tid":771861,"uid":10715,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:55:32.000Z","msg":"其實應該係塊肉已經有啲問題 佢煮熟哂先敢比你食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:57:59.000Z","msg":"屌 好撚嬲呀⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食咗舊屎咁 淨係知冇牛味 好似香口膠咁！"},{"pid":"f7d2b1bad868f07b6fd1f9104f499a00c71b50e4","tid":771861,"uid":150775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"從來唔覺得出街食貴嘅野質素會成正比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d2b7d1790f43cd6b5ce67d7d26acae6a74fba2","tid":771861,"uid":99733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:59:41.000Z","msg":"澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19870f64ce9f29c8447ae54c4b60d5470d09712b","tid":771861,"uid":31266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7d2b1bad868f07b6fd1f9104f499a00c71b50e4","tid":771861,"uid":150775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"從來唔覺得出街食貴嘅野質素會成正比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,